              "blocks": {
                "q1_faq01a1": {
                  "type": "_accordion",
                  "settings": {
                    "title": "What hair types are these products best for?",
                    "content": "<p>Both products work across hair types, from fine to thick. Texture Powder is built for shorter to medium cuts where root lift and defined separation matter most. Matte Clay is built for thicker hair and longer styles where hold and shape have to last. Both are invisible on every hair color, including dark hair. No white cast, no chalk.</p>",
                    "initially_open": true
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "q2_faq01a2": {
                  "type": "_accordion",
                  "settings": {
                    "title": "Will my hair feel stiff or dry?",
                    "content": "<p>Neither. Both formulas are designed to move with your hair, not lock it in place. Hold without crunch.</p>",
                    "initially_open": false
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "q3_faq01a3": {
                  "type": "_accordion",
                  "settings": {
                    "title": "Can I restyle through the day?",
                    "content": "<p>Yes. Both products remain workable after application. Run your hands through and reshape as needed.</p>",
                    "initially_open": false
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                },
                "q4_faq01a4": {
                  "type": "_accordion",
                  "settings": {
                    "title": "What's in the formula, and what's left out?",
                    "content": "<p>Clean ingredients. No sulfates, parabens, or artificial fragrance. Full ingredient list available on each product page.</p>",
                    "initially_open": false
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "q1_faq01a1",
                "q2_faq01a2",
                "q3_faq01a3",
                "q4_faq01a4"
              ]
            }
